abstract: Job-Me leverages cutting-edge AI to revolutionize the hiring process, significantly reducing time and costs for firms. By combining advanced text mining and generative AI techniques, the system parses resumes, extracts and standardizes skills, and evaluates their relevance to job profiles. Leveraging large language models (LLMs) and the innovative spike model, Job-Me enhances the precision of matching job seekers with employers, ensuring an efficient and seamless recruitment experience.
